Active users refer to users with a status of 'active' in the users table; 
 The protein content is calculated in grams (g); 
 The 'veg' recipes are those with a food category of 'veg' in the recipes table.

- "easy" refers to recipes with a difficulty level of 'easy'; 
- "veg" or "non-veg" are common food categories; 
- "active users" means users with a status of 'active' in the system; 
- "top-level categories" refer to categories with no parent category.

sql:
SELECT recipe_name, preparation_time, cook_time
FROM recipes
WHERE author_id = (SELECT user_id FROM users WHERE user_name = 'Alice Johnson');
